Harvard Place received federal, state, local, and private funding for the renovation, and operates under the U.S. Department of Housing and Urban Development&rsquo;s (HUD) Section 202 supportive housing program for low-income seniors. The 22-unit building is within walking distance of multiple services and amenities located in Central Square in Cambridge.&nbsp;
