RENEW Energy Partners is an energy finance company committed to addressing the challenges of climate change by accelerating the adoption of energy-efficiency solutions. The company has raised successive multi-million-dollar capital pools from &quot;impact investors&quot; which it uses, in combination with its turnkey energy-efficiency services and industry partnerships, to fully fund and execute energy-efficiency projects for building owners.

RENEW maintains a network of national and local partners to facilitate the implementation of deep energy efficiency retrofits, which RENEW fully funds and maintains in exchange for services fees for delivered services. By designing this service fee to be lower than the energy savings we generate, our customers see immediate reduction in both their energy usage and energy spend, all while maintaining their capital and debt for business needs.
